data.title: Match complet | Boston Uprising contre Houston Outlaws | OWL 2020 | Semaine 3 | Jours 3
data.description:
La semaine 3 de l'Overwatch League 2020 aura lieu en direct de Washington D.C. les 22 et 23 février sur YouTube Gaming. Durant ces deux jours, vous pourrez suivre Washington Justice, New York Excelsior, Philadelphia Fusion, Boston Uprising, Houston Outlaws, Paris Eternal, Toronto Defiant et London Spitfire. Qui d'Excelsior ou Fusion s'approprieront la première place ? Spitfire ou Outlaws obtiendront-ils leur première victoire de la saison ? Restez connecté pour le savoir !

Learn more: www.overwatchleague.com
Suivez toute l'action: www.youtube.com/overwatchleague

data.title: Full Match | New York Excelsior vs Houston Outlaws | Overwatch League 2020 | Week 3 | Day 2
data.description:
Week 3 of the 2020 Overwatch League season is live from Washington D.C. on February 22 and 23 on YouTube Gaming. The two-day homestand features the Washington Justice, New York Excelsior, Philadelphia Fusion, Boston Uprising, Houston Outlaws, Paris Eternal, Toronto Defiant, and London Spitfire. Will the Excelsior or the Fusion make that first place spot their own? Can the Spitfire or the Outlaws get their first win of the season? Tune in to find out!
 
Join us for the 2020 Overwatch season

It's all part of Insights: powered by Intel. Want more Insights? Visit https://overwatchleague.com/en-us/intel-insights.

data.title: Brenjamin Franklin’s Tour of Old Philadelphia

data.title: My Hero: Winston

data.title: Toronto Defiant RoKy and Aid Do Yoga: Access Granted
data.description: Malik Forté swings by the Toronto Defiant house to pick up RoKy and Aid for an afternoon of yoga with a special instructor. One of these players is a master of dance and the other is a Ping Pong monster. Find out which is which in this episode of Access Granted presented by Toyota.

data.title: Game/Set with the Shanghai Dragons’ Dding
data.description: Sneak your way into a massive teamfight with DDing of the Shanghai Dragons, as we take an in-depth look at his settings when playing Sombra. With these tips you’ll be swinging fights with massive EMPs. This is Game/Set brought to you by OMEN by HP.

data.title: Enter the Dragons
data.description: Ushering in the 2-2-2 meta early in Stage 3 and capping it off with a Stage Final win, the Shanghai Dragons are confident that Stage 4 is where the Dragons will breathe the most fire.
